{"tid":900000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國稱殲-20飛行表演令人驚嘆     專家：用的是俄國引擎","createTime":"2018-11-13T01:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T12:00:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0a49951ef9b519b1dda7354e78e0e1fc2c030b12","tid":900000,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpodmrCR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpodmrCR.jpg&h=242397b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國廣東珠海舉行「2018第十二屆中國國際航空航天博覽會」，全新隱形戰機殲-20於昨天（11日）展開飛行表演，官媒《新華社》稱整個過程令人驚嘆，但軍事專家立刻打臉，直指這款第4代戰鬥機的引擎似乎並非中國製造，而是來自俄羅斯。<br />\n<br />\n據《CNN》報導，兩架殲-20飛過中國航空展時，人群中不斷傳來興奮的尖叫聲，戰機的飛彈艙門是打開的，露出裡面的4枚遠程導彈，兩側機翼也各裝了1枚導彈。<br />\n<br />\n中國解放軍英文網站在今年稍早時指出，未來若有任何對手敢挑戰中國，殲-20就會與之交戰，並宣稱殲-20改變了亞太地區的空中力量平衡，因為在過去只有日本這樣的美國盟友部署了隱形戰機，但到了現在，中國殲-20將打破這樣的壟斷場面。<br />\n<br />\n不過，前澳洲軍官、格里菲斯亞洲研究院研究員萊頓（Peter Layton）表示，在殲-20上並沒有看到中國的引擎，這代表中國仍難以掌握先進的噴射引擎技術。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中國解放軍英文網站於今天（12日）宣布，中國戰機已具備推力向量的引擎技術，但萊頓繼續打臉，他坦言「如果殲-20隱型戰機在飛行中顯示出推力向量，那將會令人印象深刻，但事實並非如此。」萊頓說，中國的推力向量仍然落後了10年至20年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2609750\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2609750&d=53WRbafYR%2FlBXwOwb%2Bn%2BKEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a1bdc08d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2609750&h=b9e9b1f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2609750</a>"},{"pid":"6e7b44dc7275a20f13751b35baec53f5865ad1bb","tid":900000,"uid":54373,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:41:25.000Z","msg":"飛行開到彈夾<br />\n已經大J特J <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9434c9d7b80650ba0f0d79cd896921402da64e2e","tid":900000,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:44:54.000Z","msg":"未來若有任何對手敢挑戰中國，殲-20就會與之交戰，並宣稱殲-20改變了亞太地區的空中力量平衡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7e9518166cc573eb8244bd0a40cf38a8c34830","tid":900000,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:48:56.000Z","msg":"買人野當自己自煮燃發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9f2974bbc6e1b171c8a89ece1a189ca4380f39","tid":900000,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:51:22.000Z","msg":"太行呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69625bac1a8fc0f16ae261055ad03b9cb8110146","tid":900000,"uid":10064,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:51:25.000Z","msg":"你估下佢地飛個時美軍雷達睇唔睇到？<br />\n或者人地架F22係你頭頂呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a49e51d87decd922a15c021e6e2ca2a08bd4206","tid":900000,"uid":2442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"df7e9518166cc573eb8244bd0a40cf38a8c34830","tid":900000,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:48:56.000Z","msg":"買人野當自己自煮燃發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:52:05.000Z","msg":"買埋離抄都抄唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4379fd5564748125232d7e4dce7fa3fac1089521","tid":900000,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:54:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a12ff918b626e730199fdb252b283f7303f69c4e","tid":900000,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4379fd5564748125232d7e4dce7fa3fac1